<div style="background-color:#7a056e; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; margin-left:20px;">RESERVATIONS & ACCOMMODATION</div>
<div style="background-color:#7c7c7c; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; margin-left:20px;">2. BONUS BOOKINGS</div>
<div style="background-color:#b8b8b8; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; margin-left:20px;">What is a Bonus booking?</div>
<p style="padding:0px 20px 0px 40px;">A Bonus booking is a reservation made in Rands, rather than using Club Units for out of Peak season periods, subject to Bonus booking accommodation periods being available.</p>